qas.question: What date was Saint FM radio launched?
What date was Saint FM radio closed?
Which newspaper is the sister company of Saint FM radio?

context: Saint FM provided a local radio service for the island which was also available on internet radio and relayed in Ascension Island. The station was not government funded. It was launched in <a0_0>January 2005<a0_0/> and closed on <a1_0>21 December 2012<a1_0/>. It broadcast news, features and music in collaboration with its sister newspaper, the <a2_0>St Helena Independent<a2_0/> (which continues).
